==1980年代至今==
* 日本[[朝日新聞|朝日新聞]]在1980年1月報導了陸軍上尉中晴文夫仍然躲藏在[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]的阿爾孔山。一個由中晴文夫過去的同袍宮澤功所領導的搜尋隊相信他們發現了中晴的小屋。<ref>[[Asahi_Shimbun|Asahi Shimbun]], January 18, 1980</ref><ref>{{Citation | format = PDF | publisher = Fulton History | url = http://fultonhistory.com/Newspaper%2011/Geneva%20NY%20Finger%20Lake%20Times/Geneva%20NY%20Finger%20Lake%20Times%201980%20Apr%201980/Geneva%20NY%20Finger%20Lake%20Times%201980%20Apr%201980%20-%200296.pdf | title = Still fighting, 35 years after V-J day | newspaper = Finger Lakes Times | date = April 10, 1980 | page = 1 | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | archive-date = 2012-05-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120513141753/http://fultonhistory.com/Newspaper%2011/Geneva%20NY%20Finger%20Lake%20Times/Geneva%20NY%20Finger%20Lake%20Times%201980%20Apr%201980/Geneva%20NY%20Finger%20Lake%20Times%201980%20Apr%201980%20-%200296.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation | publisher = Google News | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1368&dat=19800405&id=J3pQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AxIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6758,842754 | title = Soldier's hut found in Philippines | newspaper = Milwaukee Sentinel | date = April 5, 1980, part 1 | page = 3 | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | archive-date = 2016-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160519203254/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1368&dat=19800405&id=J3pQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AxIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6758,842754 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 宮澤功已經尋找中晴文夫好幾年了。<ref>{{cite journal|last=宮沢|first=功|title=連載 サラリーマン男のロマン ミンドロ島戦友捜索奮戦記|journal=実業之日本|year=1957|volume=83|issue=6|pages=102-105|publisher=[[Jitsugyo_no_Nihon_Sha|Jitsugyo no Nihon Sha]]}}</ref>然而，沒有證據顯示中晴文夫居住到如新聞所說的1980年之久。
* 在1981年，一個[[日本國會|日本國會]]的委員會提到了報紙有報導在[[索羅門群島|索羅門群島]]的[[維拉拉維拉島|維拉拉維拉島]]上叢林中仍有殘留兵的存在，並且搜尋隊進行了超過十年的調查但是資訊太過貧乏而無法進一步的搜尋。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/SENTAKU/sangiin/094/1200/09404141200007c.html |title=第０９４回国会 社会労働委員会 第７号 昭和五十六年四月十四日（火曜日） |publisher=Kokkai.ndl.go.jp |date= |accessdate=2014-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104212646/http://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/SENTAKU/sangiin/094/1200/09404141200007c.html |archive-date=2014-01-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
